# Docker Integration, Shop Sync & Performance Walkthrough

I have successfully integrated Docker, synchronized the Shop design, optimized desktop performance, streamlined the layout, and added new feature sections (Partners, Visual Script Builder).

## 1. Visual Script Builder (Live Demo)
- **Node Graph UI**: Visual scripting interface matching the **zigzag/waterfall reference**.
- **Features**:
  - **Variables Overlay**: Prominent orange button for variable management.
  - **Grid Background**: Dark detailed grid for precise alignment.
- **Connections**:
  - **Green (Success)**: Main execution path (Start -> Open URL -> ... -> If).
  - **Red (Error/Stop)**: Specific path from "If" (Red Port) to "Stop".
- **Styling**: Green Start node, Blue Action nodes, precise port colors.
- **Simulation**: Real-time execution loop traces the path.

